      {
        "id": 260885,
        "name": "anon53652",
        "username": "anon53652",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/anon53652/{size}/11044_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-02-10T10:42:36.232Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I agree. I translated a 100+ page document with quite some custom macros and a lot of physics equations from LaTeX to MathJax and that went quite smooth.</p>\n<p>Btw, do you know how MathJax deals with other fonts like Rune and hyroglyphics?</p>",
        "post_number": 10,
